title: Beloved - Toni Morrison
description:
This is Toni Morrison's award-winning novel. I apologize for the strange PDF formatting - the pages have numbers at the bottom, but there isn't one page per PDF. If anyone knows how to fix this, I'll re-upload, but hopefully it isn't too bothersome. This is my first torrent, by the way! I've been a user for a long time, and I always seed for a long time after I download, but I've never had something that there wasn't already a torrent of.
Oh, and I should mention, don't read this book unless you want an unpleasant experience because it is quite bad in my opinion.
